dead in the pond.

51:43.562 --> 51:46.112
And all the plants are dying.

51:50.944 --> 51:53.494
Can we bury Chil and Bill in the sea?

51:53.906 --> 51:54.906
In the sea?

51:56.074 --> 51:59.584
Piki said people in India
get buried in the sea.

51:59.620 --> 52:01.200
Of course. Yes, we can.

52:01.246 --> 52:03.086
How about you go get something
to bury them in?

52:13.133 --> 52:15.093
You should have worn white.

52:15.135 --> 52:17.095
I wore a white scarf. That's not enough?

52:17.137 --> 52:18.137
No.

52:18.639 --> 52:21.469
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to be rude
to Chil and Bill.

52:22.476 --> 52:24.476
It's a good spot right here.

52:31.360 --> 52:33.820
Bye-bye, Chil. Bye-bye, Bill.

52:40.118 --> 52:42.118
Mommy, who's that man?

52:44.164 --> 52:45.604
It's all right, baby. He's far away.

52:45.791 --> 52:47.131
Not that man, Mommy!

52:47.167 --> 52:48.167
That man!

53:03.851 --> 53:06.311
Why did that man put ash on your face?

53:06.353 --> 53:07.653
I don't know, love.

53:07.688 --> 53:08.978
Did I get it all?

53:09.022 --> 53:10.022
Yeah, you got it.

53:10.983 --> 53:11.983
Yeah?

53:47.936 --> 53:49.396
Luce stay behind me.

54:58.340 --> 54:59.630
Oliver?

55:03.720 --> 55:05.720
Oliver, do you want to play?

55:12.980 --> 55:17.230
Are you coming out to play, Stanley?

55:17.818 --> 55:19.028
